<section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-medium text-charcoal mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-charcoal-light text-lg mb-8">Last updated: February 2025</p>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="card mb-8">
        <p class="text-charcoal-light text-lg"><strong class="text-charcoal">The short version:</strong> We collect only what we need to help you stay connected. We never sell your data. We never share your contact lists with anyone.</p>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Information you provide</h3>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Your name, email, and phone number when you sign up</li>
        <li>Names and optional notes about people you want to stay in touch with</li>
        <li>Your preferences for how often you want to connect with different people</li>
        <li>Messages you send to Bethany via SMS</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Information we collect automatically</h3>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>When you last interacted with your contacts (so we know when to nudge you)</li>
        <li>Basic usage data like when you signed up and last used the service</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>To send you nudges about people who might be slipping off your radar</li>
        <li>To generate personalized message suggestions</li>
        <li>To improve the service and fix bugs</li>
        <li>To respond to your questions and support requests</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">What We Don't Do</h2>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>We never sell your personal information</li>
        <li>We never share your contact lists with advertisers or third parties</li>
        <li>We never read your actual text messages to your contacts (only messages sent to Bethany)</li>
        <li>We never contact your friends or family without your explicit action</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light">We use industry-standard encryption to protect your data in transit and at rest. Your PIN is hashed and never stored in plain text. We regularly review our security practices.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light">We keep your data as long as you have an active account. If you delete your account, we'll remove your personal data within 30 days, except where we're required by law to retain it.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light mb-4">You can:</p>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
        <li>Ask us to delete your data</li>
        <li>Update or correct your information</li>
        <li>Opt out of promotional communications</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light mt-4">To exercise any of these rights, text "HELP" to Bethany or email us.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light">We use the following services to operate Bethany:</p>
      <ul class="text-charcoal-light space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
        <li><strong>SendBlue</strong> — for SMS messaging</li>
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — for payment processing (if you upgrade)</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — for hosting and infrastructure</li>
        <li><strong>Anthropic Claude</strong> — for generating message suggestions</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light">We may update this policy from time to time. We'll notify you of significant changes by text message or email.</p>
      
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-medium text-charcoal mt-12 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-charcoal-light">Questions about this policy? Text "HELP" to Bethany, or email us at privacy@untitledpublishers.com.</p>
    </div>
